:

1. *Stojim* ispred kuće. (I am standing in front of the house.)
2. Ona je *stojala* pored mene. (She was standing next to me.)
3. *Stoje* li deca pored ograde? (Are the children standing next to the fence?)
4. Ne znam šta da *stojim*. (I don't know what to stand for.)
5. *Stojalo* je nekoliko ljudi ispred škole. (Several people were standing in front of the school.)